Skin Staplers

The D-tek skin stapler is a specialised disposable stapler used in surgery to close skin wounds in place of sutures. Stapling is much faster than suturing by hand and also more accurate and consistent. The d-tek skin stapler avoids, effectively, iatric cross-in-fections Skin Stapler are usually applied using a disposable stapler and removed with specilized stapler remover.
